      "text": "这招可是很痛的！",
      "text_original": "これは痛いわよ!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/yXQYe4F2fbaYFmbW2PJ8M7dIwj9eAJNm.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_EventLobby_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "……嗯？你叫我？",
      "text_original": "ん?なんか呼んだ?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/W0pfguKnR2b8lZ3RpebPQ1MiIIRMJmQy.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_EventLobby_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "啧，原来只是开玩笑啊。",
      "text_original": "なんだ、冷やかしか。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/Ejet2C6yEqONiRhwX0qnal2pMrm5tSme.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_EventLobby_3",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "你应该还有其他正经事要做吧？",
      "text_original": "他にやんなきゃいけないこと、あるんじゃないの?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/RA73S181Ji47LEw6GDjy2dVEUOTqrLwk.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_EventLobby_4",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "……唉。好好好，我知道了。所以有什么需要我帮忙的？",
      "text_original": "ふぅ、わかったわかった。何か手伝おうか?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/ihseTxz1CuXZJhiZaX1GQBBuHIwcX2OE.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_EventLogin_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "差不多该开始了。",
      "text_original": "そろそろ始めようかしら。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/xDXDZKOtcxAPv7n9RZpVIl4MWjJzfAgj.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_EventLogin_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "我准备好了。老师呢？",
      "text_original": "私は準備OK。先生は?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/WgePYfKOxOUwvCAkhMhGWRC2wYd7I4K1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_EventLogin_Season_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "进展相当不错嘛。",
      "text_original": "かなり進んだわね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/PQADofUFT5ym7J7AgSf6mwlP62Ow9RRg.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_EventLogin_Season_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "看样子都完成得差不多了？",
      "text_original": "もうほとんど終わった感じよね？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/fZU4KO24P2f8LsxfMnRnXhc9jSSwY5AM.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_EventLogin_Season_End",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "总之，最后还是再检查一遍吧。",
      "text_original": "一応、もっかい確認してみて?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/CN8KDQoGAXGdfAHJju71JunowQNrFho6.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_ExSkill_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "等会儿可别后悔！",
      "text_original": "後で後悔するんじゃないわよ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/SgXFqjx0BHEb1YsRDAfjKXZTVHgoxIRY.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_ExSkill_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "既然要动手……",
      "text_original": "そっちがやる気なら!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/tSl7HKX64lEI7jUqouJXZgzRUWZdpK60.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_ExSkill_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "想看我出手？那好……！",
      "text_original": "そんなに見たいなら！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/x5HOcE6D1FJbbVRLr8opbNyMWIQBlA0x.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_ExSkill_Level_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "给我看好了！",
      "text_original": "よく見てなさい!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/RFXhYygTA6FtwJLn9uv19Gl7inX3hbpp.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_ExSkill_Level_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "接招！",
      "text_original": "くらえ!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/unK6F7Pn0ylNZrdlhL8F91i1eXYVHcC4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_ExSkill_Level_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "这招如何！",
      "text_original": "これはどう?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/gs7gmLVv7FmUe5FjRYhzExXJDkr2Osy7.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_ExWeapon_Get",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "说实话，我还是觉得有点神奇……毕竟我平时不会拿着这种东西走来走去。谢谢你们……特地为我准备。我会努力回应期待的。",
      "text_original": "正直言ってちょっと珍しいというか、普段はこういうのを持ち歩いてないからさ。わざわざ用意してもらっちゃって、ありがとう。期待に応えられるよ。ちゃんとやるわね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/TJb9yz1Ele216m7MsO2XmfDcNM47AiyV.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Formation_In_1",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "啊，什么？只要参加就行了？",
      "text_original": "ん?なに?参加すればいいの?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/Sr7tB7C3MV8ZKUKQ5O2dKSIHP6k1noig.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Formation_In_2",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "需要我帮忙？这倒是没什么……",
      "text_original": "手伝ってほしいの? それくらいなら、まあ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/hfGhlcozf9q4HFNV8DEKM1dq9goF9eTU.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Formation_Select",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "怎么了？",
      "text_original": "何か用?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/hgPBVoLGUhcDSm85ktJvgyRLAYNLUZM0.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Gachaget",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "常盘台中学2年级，御坂美琴。需要我帮忙的话就跟我说吧。",
      "text_original": "ときわ台中学2年 御坂美琴。私の手伝いが必要なら言ってちょうだい。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/8SIQu1I3sR47K8QLaQVWKj1gRCVnIP7t.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Growup_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "哇，这是什么！感觉不错啊！",
      "text_original": "あ、なにこれ?いいんじゃない?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/BUvE12Erl7FPQPAx9scC2kMBbxWHe0dL.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Growup_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "感觉头脑变得清醒了，谢谢！",
      "text_original": "頭がすっきりする感じね。ありがとう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/XwtJdFF7lhEHuyn9qtqj6FWmdq8yOvUg.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Growup_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "就这么送给我？我，我是无所谓……",
      "text_original": "こんなにいいの? 私はいいんだけど…",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/VAqkeujVmwIHoOpjFA68mxgLRqNKOPrE.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Growup_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "你帮了我，我也会报答你的！",
      "text_original": "手助けしてくれた分、ちゃんと返していくから!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/E4mVRb2ORJ1lkXzPloK0j6jvVIgwrrxP.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Lobby_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "总觉得一个人出门对我来说还有点困难……",
      "text_original": "なんとなーく、一人で出かけるのはまだハードル高いというか…",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/TPmo6HKPeVcmIucszTKfk20RUzYIq2IG.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Lobby_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "希望停电的时候我能来帮帮忙？啊啊，是在开玩笑吧？……不过，的确也能帮就是了。",
      "text_original": "停電の時に助けてほしい?はいはい、冗談でしょ?まあ、助けなくもないけどさ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/IV2UVAcx12fkVg9bXkd0wPbBBObHLEj0.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Lobby_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "时不时就会觉得，这里和学园都市好像啊。",
      "text_original": "たまーに学園都市に似てると感じることがあるんだよね、ここ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/TqqadTsWUGHQBi9EAFw3JAiWulvp8UeV.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Lobby_4",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师，有空的话要不要去吹吹风？",
      "text_original": "先生、よかったら風邪にあたらない?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/hvW9aDsiM78mFvNZzeLSDid12nNsJjIG.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Lobby_5",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这里有好多会说话的猫……到底是怎么回事？啊，没什么！真的没什么！",
      "text_original": "ここって喋る猫も多いわよね。一体どういうことなのかしら。あ、いや、なんでもない。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/WxqCqHiKL1EFj0iwu5QoFOAGlE54cg6a.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_LogIn_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "啊，老师，这边，我在这边。你怎么才来啊，我都等好久了。",
      "text_original": "あ、先生、こっちこっち。ちょっと来るの遅いわよ。待ってたんだから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/zhMsfJydmAEv44pgTpBfkbfYIc7fm6bf.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_LogIn_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "辛苦了，老师。我？我一直在这里啊。",
      "text_original": "お疲れ様先生。私?ずっとここにいたけど?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/yyrrx2lYxIa1T1qQRPU0p27TWiJTDihG.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_MemorialLobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "唔唔唔~~~",
      "text_original": "うぅぅぅぅぅぅ~~",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/3y3V0vt31W2LEsnECRKPIHLpFQTI9DoT.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_MemorialLobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这样一直看着它，就感觉它好像变可爱了一点……",
      "text_original": "ずっと眺めてたら、ちょっとは可愛く見えてきたような?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/Fjl7jl1Qwqch4zOvLYHMV9PidQ0vAza8.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_MemorialLobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "所以说，它是猪……？还是河马？",
      "text_original": "結局これは豚なの?それともカバ?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/UbRIs5lXXb0rW9x6s02jqjKAmIlZlK9F.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_MemorialLobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……诶？！是鸟？！不可能吧？！",
      "text_original": "え?鳥?嘘でしょ!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/jj42r2oEl1Yao81SoVslrKysTuq7EhL3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_MemorialLobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "话，话是这么说……",
      "text_original": "そ、それはそうだけど…",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/XAPblIkxqcNMOZ4dFpwu8LYVFy5vHLD3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_MemorialLobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "哈哈……算了，是什么都无所谓。",
      "text_original": "あははは、まぁどっちでもいいわ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/IeDlSA5CPX0HfebVOYlujwGpbMKOIbof.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_MemorialLobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "而且，仔细想想……",
      "text_original": "というか、よく考えたら…",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/JbCOx3hB2jrxoXBQvSZTEjR4g00DGgko.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_MemorialLobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这可是老师送我的礼物呢。",
      "text_original": "これ、先生からのプレゼントなのよね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/O5LR9R1cIYg8Ony67KnK7gFaWIlkrdlU.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_MemorialLobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……我会好好爱惜的。",
      "text_original": "大切にするわ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/3dzhzNk6I5D6wDBKgFR8P0tHl2iC698g.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_MemorialLobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "谢谢你，老师。",
      "text_original": "ありがとう、先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/NrWmQl88ogy70kdxO35Bx89EqV5u1pPo.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Relationship_Up_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "总觉得一直在欠你人情……这样没关系吗？",
      "text_original": "なんかずっともらってばっかだけどいいの?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/BjweoOCKqE386OH8NSsZnqiPiMd5hMeV.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Relationship_Up_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "感觉都有点不好意思了……谢谢你，你的好意我收到了。",
      "text_original": "ちょっと照れくさいかも まあありがたくもらうけど。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/stWfMDCZn9O6JspjpaPPZPi4xPowYSc9.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Relationship_Up_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "偶尔这样也不错呢，嗯。",
      "text_original": "たまにはこういうのも悪くないわよね。うん。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/j6rI1M5UdjLJSjFbBjtRe0LOPl9IZ6kb.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Relationship_Up_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "我也想帮你做点什么……唔……有什么我能帮上忙的吗？",
      "text_original": "私も何かしたいんだけど、その、手伝えることあるかしら?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/FdWgQcGSz35U4B5wmyHa1REcaRqb8KT0.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Season_Birthday",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "诶？噢，谢谢。没想到生日也会在这儿度过啊……啊哈哈……感觉心情有点复杂呢。",
      "text_original": "えっ? あ、ありがとう。まさか誕生日もここで過ごすことになるなんて…。えへへ。ちょっと複雑な気持ちだわ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/fk8E3GkIV5cRegsDVEx61jqinwDOCLqI.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Season_Birthday_Player",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "哟！老师，你今天生日？生日快乐！有没有什么想要的？",
      "text_original": "おー、先生今日誕生日?おめでと。何か欲しいものある?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/B8ALsuGI6E75RakveOBDyVcTh2oZrD9m.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Season_Halloween",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "外面好闹腾啊。这样的日子，一般都会出很多事情……",
      "text_original": "なんか外が騒がしいわね。こんな日は、なんかいろいろ起こるのよね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/Gx9AFPpeafdBly0cvIHJorjVZzM1r0dt.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Season_NewYear",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "新年快乐，老师！说起来，这边过新年的时候都会做些什么？",
      "text_original": "あけましておめでとう先生。あ、そういえば、ここでは新年は何をして過ごすの?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/5PXxFnU2CjZxMbdfMrmzrj9zV68CASkN.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Season_Xmas",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "圣诞节……原来这里也会过啊。老师有和谁约好一起出门吗？",
      "text_original": "クリスマスかぁ、こっちでもお祝いするのね。先生は出かける約束とかある?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/qzyPKAPH3huBTzqhS0PiWmpjDQvsOlNM.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Tactic_Defeat_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "咕……好、好奇怪……",
      "text_original": "ぐっ……お、おかしいな……",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/P0MmSm3wycZFy4kbDNpzvyoPHtD5u9JP.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Tactic_Defeat_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "比想象中要难一点啊……",
      "text_original": "思ったより難しかったわね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/AM0ePS6ZlEUjw1h3y63l8vBOtnfNikuZ.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Tactic_In_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "好，我们上吧。",
      "text_original": "よし、行くわよ!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/9zRWKNHbMoYS4Nsuzk4GrEhjGX5DxTsv.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Tactic_In_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "是去这儿吗？OK。",
      "text_original": "ここに行くの?OK!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/ZdtRF34ra39rZC0uwZ8S7vrbnGQLsTNe.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Tactic_Victory_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "那就出发吧！",
      "text_original": "じゃあ出発するよ！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/lBUAQGXZztaY3uhLOVUNWz665kpPcs0k.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Tactic_Victory_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "感觉……还挺多的？",
      "text_original": "なんか多かったわね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/3yQEnefG3myaDYIaVbMHcH9wQmuZ5K2p.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9998_Title",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "蔚蓝档案！",
      "text_original": "ブルーアーカイブ",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E5%BE%A1%E5%9D%82%20%E7%BE%8E%E7%90%B4/2DQEzSX9x5T3TFuZ9azKW3QaWG0dDXOt.ogg"
    }
  ],
